reviewText: The collection is fine, although Discovery puts minimal work into these - content is just the episodes and nothing else. Amazon needs to do a better job of packing DVDs to protect during shipping - this arrived with a cracked case.
Our entire family enjoy ALL the Mythbusters dvds.  We own them all.
Very cute as advertised and very fast shipping.
Passed all expectations...Same exciting episodes as usual ..
My grand kids love watching the crew try and figure out how it is done and whether it can be done....
